<p class="written-japanese">æ±äº¬ã€€ã‚ã€€ã ã„ã¨ã—ã€€ãªã®ã§ã€€ï¼ˆãã“ã€€ã«ï¼‰ã„ããŸã„ã€€ã§ã™</p>
<p>In this sentence, we donâ€™t necessarily need <strong>â€œsoko niâ€</strong>, it can be taken out if wanted. <strong>â€œNanodeâ€</strong> means <strong>â€œso that/that's whyâ€</strong>.</p>
<p>For my second sentence, I shouldâ€™ve written something like this:</p>
